data.text: Sore arm almost straight after the jab. Will see over the next few days what else develops but generally feeling 100% since getting the vaccine. The sore arm is a new phenomenon!

@Kanye_WestTD We need to get greater equity and  equality - we live in a connected world- with wealth and resources- if Covid teaches us anything it is that a problem or issue in the remotest parts of the world is all our problem and issue - same with climate
@HughGillanders Definitely! The horrific truth right now is that I, a 19 year old, get a vaccine faster than most 90 (!) Year olds around the world which is simply wrong.
@Kanye_WestTD Congratulations- great initiative- we need vaccine equity
